Mountain Province Diamonds Inc.


            
            Mountain Province Diamonds, Inc. engages in the mining and exploration business. It focuses on diamond assets in Gahcho Kué in the Northwest region. The company was founded by Shatzko Paul on December 2, 1986 and is headquartered in Toronto, Canada.

            
